ology used to justify the Guantánamo Bay detention center, the torture and enhanced interrogation of enemy combatants, and the American carceral state.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 0aWar crime trialszGuamxHistoryy20th century. 0aWorld War, 1939-1945xAtrocitieszGuam. 7aHISTORY / Modern / 20th Century.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978147800566740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781478005667423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9781478005667/original  aEBA_DUK_ALL  aEBA_DUK_EALL  aEBA_DUK_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles